        <Parent_String>hammers (tools) [300024823], striking tools [300024822], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
